                <h1>"Choosing the Perfect Non-Distracting Background"</h1>
                <p>A non-distracting background is essential for keeping the focus on the subject, whether it's for photography, video conferencing, or presentations. Subtle colors, soft textures, and minimal patterns help eliminate distractions, allowing viewers to absorb the key message. Choose backgrounds that enhance rather than compete with your content for a professional look.</p>
